44' Ronaldinho
Stadium: Olímpico
Grêmio: Danrlei; Itaqui, Ronaldo Alves, Émerson, Éder e Roger; Capitão,
Fabinho (Djair) e Ronaldinho; Rodrigo Gral (Cleison) e Agnaldo (Zé Afonso).
Internacional: André; Enciso, Lúcio, Gonçalves, Régis (Almir) e Elivélton;
Ânderson (João Santos), Dunga e Claiton; Fabiano (Manoel) e Christian.
Referee: Carlos Simon, with Flávio Teixeira and Sílvio Silva.
Revenue: R$481.288,00  
Attendance: 34.655

Top Scorer: Ronaldinho (Grêmio) with 15 goals.

[Ronaldinho is also known as Ronald(inh)o Assis or Ronald(inh)o Gaucho.]


